snippet: No. 1 Kentucky labored through an 18-turnover performance in which L.S.U. never trailed by more than 9 before the Wildcats closed out a 60-51 win.
abstract: College Basketball Men's Roundup; Kentucky defeats Louisiana State, 60-51, in the Southeastern Conference tournament quarterfinals; other men's and women's tournament results noted.
lead_paragraph: No. 1 Kentucky labored through an 18-turnover performance in which L.S.U. never trailed by more than 9 before the Wildcats closed out a 60-51 win.

headline.main: Calipari and No. 1 Kentucky Stumble Past L.S.U.; Baylor Stuns Kansas
headline.print_headline: Kentucky Stumbles Past L.S.U.; Baylor Stuns Kansas
